export default class User {
    /**
     * User informations
     *
     * @param { number } id
     * @param { string } firstName
     * @param { string } lastName
     * @param { number } age
     * @param { number } score
     */
    constructor(id, firstName, lastName, age, score) {
        this.userId = id
        this.firstName = firstName
        this.lastName = lastName
        this.age = age
        this.score = score
    }
}
